						<div id="post-53851969965" class="hentry post posttype-text odd first-post ">
							
								
									<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://blog.watsi.org/post/53851969965/happy-arbitrary-day" title="Happy Arbitrary Day!" rel="bookmark">Happy Arbitrary Day!</a></h2>
								
											
							
							<div class="entry-content">
								<!-- google_ad_section_start -->
								<p>In honor of the best made-up holiday in existence, Redditors have collectively funded 21 medical treatments on Watsi. </p>
<p><a href="https://watsi.org/" target="_blank"><img alt="image" src="http://media.tumblr.com/ebe369761d9096b6cceb4fdfab88e7a6/tumblr_inline_moykfaOaab1qz4rgp.png"/></a></p>

<p>But they didn&#8217;t stop at funding life-changing medical care. <a href="http://redditgifts.com/gallery/" target="_blank">Check out the awesome gifts they&#8217;re sending each other</a>.</p>
<p>What could be better than a day dedicated to sending strangers gifts for no other reason than it makes everyone happy?</p>
								<!-- google_ad_section_end -->
							</div><!-- .entry-content -->
						<!-- Metadata follows... -->
					
					

					

					
					
					
					
					
					
					
					
					
					
					
				
				
					
				
				
					
				
				
					
				
				
