								<a href="http://blog.watsi.org/post/53851969965/happy-arbitrary-day" title="Permalink for this post" rel="bookmark"><span class="published">25. June 2013</span></a>
								
						
								
								
								
									<span class="meta-sep meta-sep-tags separator">&middot; </span>
									<span class="comment-link">
										<a class="dsq-comment-count" href="http://blog.watsi.org/post/53851969965/happy-arbitrary-day#disqus_thread">Comments</a>
