						<div id="post-51161491138" class="hentry post posttype-text odd ">
							
								
									<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://blog.watsi.org/post/51161491138/karmabox-launches-watsi-widget" title="Karmabox launches Watsi widget" rel="bookmark">Karmabox launches Watsi widget</a></h2>
								
											
							
							<div class="entry-content">
								<!-- google_ad_section_start -->
								<p></p>

<p></p>
<p>Many of you have asked for this, and it&#8217;s finally here!</p>
<p><a href="http://karmabox.io/" target="_blank"><img src="http://media.tumblr.com/d347d38876e7f1fe88c1daaa7b77f360/tumblr_inline_mn9k1oh66B1qz4rgp.png"/></a></p>

<p>With <a href="http://karmabox.io/" target="_blank">Karmabox</a>, anyone can <a href="http://karmabox.io/" target="_blank">embed a widget</a> on their website to help fund medical treatments for people in need.</p>
<p><a href="http://karmabox.io/" target="_blank"><img src="http://media.tumblr.com/af7d7fd635c6cf100144ba4faba4209d/tumblr_inline_mn9k28vKQ11qz4rgp.png"/></a></p>

<p></p>
<p><a href="http://karmabox.io" target="_blank"><span>Get the Watsi widget.</span></a></p>
<p><span>We are blown away by people who donate their time and talents to create awesome things for Watsi. Thank you to our friends <a href="http://www.manuelmeurer.com/" target="_blank">Manuel</a> and <a href="http://www.jenny-lettow.de/" target="_blank">Jenny</a> for making this happen!</span></p>
<p>Add the Watsi widget to your website at <a href="http://karmabox.io/" target="_blank">karmabox.io</a></p>
