									<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://blog.watsi.org/post/49377008100/i-decided-to-donate-all-of-my-tips-to-this-little-dude" title=""I decided to donate all of my tips to this little dude on Watsi. It&#8217;s not pretty, but it seems to be going well."" rel="bookmark">"I decided to donate all of my tips to this little dude on Watsi. It&#8217;s not pretty, but it seems to be going well."</a></h2>
								
											
							
							<div class="entry-content">
								<!-- google_ad_section_start -->
								<p><a href="https://watsi.org/profile/91964860222f-brian" target="_blank"><img src="http://media.tumblr.com/b800d990e0399c1eed14065dd6144491/tumblr_inline_mm4wticYUm1qz4rgp.jpg"/></a></p>

