						<div class="entry-meta post-meta-data">
							<p class="entry-meta-line">
								<a href="http://blog.watsi.org/post/49377008100/i-decided-to-donate-all-of-my-tips-to-this-little-dude" title="Permalink for this post" rel="bookmark"><span class="published">1. May 2013</span></a>
								
						
								
								
								
